➜周杰伦快手直播首秀，用魔术为你调了一杯 Mojito
https://www.ifanr.com/1354167?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	53052
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354252" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Jy8675NW78S7Zr_Aarb9n0ff5Mh5DJQ4.jpg" alt="" width="1276" height="638" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Jy8675NW78S7Zr_Aarb9n0ff5Mh5DJQ4.jpg 1276w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Jy8675NW78S7Zr_Aarb9n0ff5Mh5DJQ4-360x180.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Jy8675NW78S7Zr_Aarb9n0ff5Mh5DJQ4-768x384.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Jy8675NW78S7Zr_Aarb9n0ff5Mh5DJQ4-1024x512.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1276px) 100vw, 1276px" /></span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">账号上线不到 6 天，粉丝突破 1000 万。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">涨粉速度这么快，在视频中宣称「当粉丝达到 1000 万的时候，我会表演最强的魔术直播」的周杰伦可能也没预料到，以至于如今粉丝都突破 2000 万了，在快手的首场直播才姗姗来迟。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">不过，还好我们等到了。</span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354168" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG15.jpeg" alt="" width="816" height="1192" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG15.jpeg 816w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG15-360x526.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG15-768x1122.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG15-701x1024.jpeg 701w" sizes="(max-width: 816px) 100vw, 816px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">和预告视频所说的一样，周杰伦快手首场直播内容以魔术表演为主，直播嘉宾则是周杰伦的魔术师朋友陈冠霖和蔡威泽（Will）。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">看完这场魔术直播，我开始相信周杰伦玩魔术比音乐还久了。</span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-8061273" data-header="3"><span class="ql-author-8061273">周杰伦直播首秀，用魔术调了一杯 Mojito </span></h3>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">「爱了爱了」「我的青春」「周杰伦、周杰伦」「无与伦比」&#8230;..</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">离直播正式开始还有半小时，直播间人气就迅速突破了 100 万，数不清的礼物和弹幕不断在刷屏，观众对这次直播的热情可见一斑。</span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354169" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG12.jpeg" alt="" width="3361" height="2156" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG12.jpeg 3361w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG12-360x231.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG12-768x493.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG12-1024x657.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3361px) 100vw, 3361px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">而除了在 App 设置多个入口为周杰伦直播造势外，快手还在北京、上海、广州等 8 个城市的地标建筑上加上了大屏广告，8 点半正式直播后还会在广州太古汇、杭州国大等 5 个城市地标大屏上全程转播周杰伦的直播首秀。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">「噢哟，有点卡住了哦，现在直播哦」</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">随着周杰伦的出现，直播间人气达到了 500 万，经过简单的直播情况确认之后。周杰伦开始了第一个魔术，只见杰伦在四张纸牌各自放了一个硬币，但随着杰伦手臂不断的晃动，纸牌下面的硬币数量也一直在变化。</span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354158" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2020-07-26-20-31-43.2020-07-26-20_39_10.gif" alt="" width="276" height="492" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">之后周杰伦干脆把纸牌拿走，在桌子上简单挥动手臂，桌子上的硬币就开始形成各种各样的图案，有数字、甚至还有硬币组成的心形圈。</span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354156" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/J1.gif" alt="" width="276" height="492" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">第一个魔术表演结束后周杰伦和冠霖、will 两位朋友聊天时也透露了为什么这么晚才直播：</span></p>
<blockquote class="ql-long-8061273">
<div class="ql-blockquote-item ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">因为最近一直在练这个酷炫的魔术，20 多天的训练才能有今天的表演效果。</span></div>
</blockquote>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354170" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG16.jpeg" alt="" width="828" height="1792" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG16.jpeg 828w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG16-360x779.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG16-768x1662.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG16-473x1024.jpeg 473w" sizes="(max-width: 828px) 100vw, 828px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">随后一行人开始和留言互动，但由于大多都是对周杰伦的夸赞、表白或者让杰伦唱歌，杰伦表示，</span><span class="ql-author-8061273">不是不唱，没有乐器，直播清唱似乎也不太好。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">直播期间各种打赏不停，礼物榜首位是时大漂亮等快手原生网红，显然是为了引流。</span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354201" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG21-1.jpeg" alt="" width="828" height="1792" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG21-1.jpeg 828w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG21-1-360x779.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG21-1-768x1662.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG21-1-473x1024.jpeg 473w" sizes="(max-width: 828px) 100vw, 828px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">没办法，由于留言一直在夸赞周杰伦，一行三人只能和周游记一样边走边聊，突然第二个魔术出现了。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">周杰伦的魔术师朋友蔡威泽突然抓住陈冠霖身上的一个蝴蝶元素，随着它把手放开，图案突然出现在了一行人背后的画上面，之后蔡威泽又握住一管黄色颜料，随着他手臂的摆动，黄色又凭空出现到了画上</span><span class="ql-author-8061273">，又一阵摆动后，画上的花又被染上了红色。</span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354161" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG331.jpeg" alt="" width="1080" height="2340" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG331.jpeg 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG331-360x780.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG331-768x1664.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG331-473x1024.jpeg 473w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">一阵惊讶、欢呼之后，轮到周杰伦的另一位魔术师朋友陈冠霖开始表演魔术了，四个人走到另外一副画前面，陈冠霖提议不如大家一起表演如何使用魔术调制一杯 Mojito 酒。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">接下来就是本场直播第三个魔术了，周杰伦用手罩住画中人物的口袋，从中抽出了一条丝巾。</span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354165" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2020-07-26-20-51-53.2020-07-26-20_54_25.gif" alt="" width="276" height="492" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">而陈冠霖则用丝巾罩住画上的香槟，一转手香槟突然出现在了他的手中。</span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354164" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/J3.gif" alt="" width="276" height="492" /></p>
<blockquote>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">Mojito 还缺什么呢？是冰块</span></p>
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">话音刚落，只见周杰伦握住杯子，画中的冰块一块一块掉落在杯子当中。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">有了冰块，还缺酒啊，接下来就是本场直播的最后两个魔术了，陈冠霖晃动了一下玻璃杯，杯子中就出现了饮料，而后大家又谈到了粉色，在陈冠霖再次晃动下，杯子中饮料又变成了粉色。</span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354163" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG332-1.jpeg" alt="" width="1080" height="2340" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG332-1.jpeg 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG332-1-360x780.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG332-1-768x1664.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG332-1-473x1024.jpeg 473w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p>随着萧敬腾推着的调酒材料出现，周杰伦和朋友们一起调制完 Mojito ，这场直播已经进行了快 30 分钟。</p>
<p>正当观众还在期待下一个节目时，周杰伦匆匆结束了本场直播，难怪直播前周杰伦就让大家别太期待了。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354202" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/12312.jpg" alt="" width="1381" height="5347" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/12312.jpg 1381w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/12312-360x1394.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/12312-768x2974.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1381px) 100vw, 1381px" /></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-8061273" data-header="3"><span class="ql-author-8061273">快手们借「周杰伦」破圈，并不容易</span></h3>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">从 5 月 29 日入驻快手，到 6 月 12 日发布新歌，再到今天的魔术直播，周杰伦和快手的合作无疑吸引了大半个中文互联网圈的注意力。这样的影响力，为快手带来的收益是显而易见的——破圈增长。</span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354172" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/MOJITO.jpg" alt="" width="1887" height="1061" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/MOJITO.jpg 1887w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/MOJITO-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/MOJITO-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/MOJITO-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1887px) 100vw, 1887px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">但引入明星对直播平台不一定全是好处，要解决的问题同样不少。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">对于快手来说，引入大量明星固然可以促进破圈增长和调和社区内容生态，但这势必会挤压快手部分原生网红的生存空间。之前快手头部网红和散打哥因全网骂战宣布退网后，辛巴就曾向快手喊话：</span></p>
<blockquote class="ql-long-8061273">
<div class="ql-blockquote-item ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">快手，我希望你们能把眼睛擦亮一点，我辛有志在大部分类目当中，可以调动整个国内的资源，请运用好我身上的本事和资源……”</span></div>
</blockquote>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354171" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3333.jpg" alt="" width="2160" height="2318" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3333.jpg 2160w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3333-360x386.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3333-768x824.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3333-954x1024.jpg 954w" sizes="(max-width: 2160px) 100vw, 2160px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">（快手头部主播 辛巴）</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">快手力推周杰伦等明星时，此消彼长下，像辛巴这样的快手原生网红得到的关注度自然就会减低。而且习惯了快手老铁文化的用户，不一定能接受大量明星的入驻，因为周杰伦涌入快手的周杰伦粉丝们，要习惯快手的老铁社区文化，同样也不容易。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">此外，直播最重要的变现方式之一电商带货也在遭受着质疑。今年年初受疫情影响，直播带货成为了互联网圈最热门的潮流，网红、明星都开始扎堆入场，但结果却各不相同。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><a class="ql-link ql-author-8061273" href="https://m.21jingji.com/article/20200708/herald/b0e305ccc887b28710ba0a14bff56045.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">据 21 世纪经济报报道</a><span class="ql-author-8061273">，商家与明星叶一茜、小沈阳的整个合作过程并不愉快，主要原因是带货数据不如人意，叶一茜直播间 90 万人观看，下单数不足 10 单，小沈阳直播间当天成交数 20 单，但第二天就退了 16 单。这对直播平台来说恐怕就不是破圈增长了，而是负增长。</span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354173" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG6.jpg" alt="" width="1645" height="3028" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG6.jpg 1645w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG6-360x663.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG6-768x1414.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WechatIMG6-556x1024.jpg 556w" sizes="(max-width: 1645px) 100vw, 1645px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲<span class="ql-author-8061273">叶一茜在微博回应直播带货事件</span></p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">直播平台 B 站，也面临着同样的问题，今年引入了大量明星的同时，也引发了不少「小破站」用户的担忧，担心入驻的明星越来越多之后会引来饭圈粉丝，导致 B 站也饭圈化，尤其是在蔡徐坤粉丝团与 B 站用户强烈对抗之后，这种抵触情绪来得更激烈。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">对此，B 站倒是做出了不少努力，今年 7 月 B 站就和蔡明老师合作推出虚拟偶像「菜菜子 Nanako」，并开启了直播首秀，令人意外的是菜菜子的声音和蔡明老师几乎一模一样，这种错位感让菜菜子的直播间很快登上了 B 站人气榜第一。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354174" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WX20200726-215724.png" alt="" width="1063" height="697" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WX20200726-215724.png 1063w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WX20200726-215724-360x236.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WX20200726-215724-768x504.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WX20200726-215724-1024x671.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1063px) 100vw, 1063px" />（</span><span class="ql-author-8061273">菜菜子 Nanako</span><span class="ql-author-8061273">)</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">菜菜子的火爆其实并不奇怪，原本 B 站就发源自 ACG 圈，社区中喜爱动漫化人物的用户大有人在，再加上蔡明老师作为春晚小品常客，在 B 站本身也十分受欢迎。这种引入明星又能适应社区文化的方式，有不小的借鉴意义。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-8061273"><span class="ql-author-8061273">对于直播平台来说，引入明星明破圈无可厚非，但如何平衡新增用户与原有社区调性是平台需要思考的。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-2673189"><span class="ql-author-2673189">周杰伦作为华语乐坛的顶流，加上快手投放的大量资源，直播首秀获得极高的关注度几乎是一件毫无疑问的事。</span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1354175" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1200_1494cdfcd6dc1-1879.jpg_1140x855.jpg" alt="" width="1140" height="855" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1200_1494cdfcd6dc1-1879.jpg_1140x855.jpg 1140w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1200_1494cdfcd6dc1-1879.jpg_1140x855-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1200_1494cdfcd6dc1-1879.jpg_1140x855-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1200_1494cdfcd6dc1-1879.jpg_1140x855-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1140px) 100vw, 1140px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-2673189"><span class="ql-author-2673189">毕竟连「过气网红」罗永浩的直播带货首秀都能卖出 1.1 亿的销售额，可如今老罗的直播带货量比起首秀已经暴跌了 97%，比起抖音投入的资源，罗永浩对抖音直播带货的带动效应不算理想。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-2673189"><span class="ql-author-2673189">快手在与抖音争夺罗永浩失败后，终于凭借周杰伦扳回一城。从新歌发布到直播首秀，无数周董歌迷一边喊着「爷青结」，一边第一次下载快手，但当中有多少人能融入快手社区，成为一起双击 666 的老铁，才是快手和周杰伦合作最终要面临的大考。</span></p>
<p>本文作者为周宇、李超凡</p>